程序包的使用
dijkstra

  • 使用dijkstra的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    dijkstra
    Contains all necessary classes for modeling algorithm Dijkstra.
    main
    Contains two core classes.
    maze
    Contains all classes for modeling the labyrinth as a two dimension array.
  • dijkstra使用的dijkstra中的类 
    类和说明
    ASetInterface
    Interface of the set A occurring in the Dijkstra algorithm as presented in the INF 101 SDA course at Telecom ParisTech The set A is a set of vertices characterized by the VertexInterface interface.
    GraphInterface
    Modeling the graph.
    PiInterface
    Interface of the pi function occuring in the Dijkstra algorithm as presented in the INF 101 SDA course at Telecom ParisTech
    PreviousInterface
    Interface of the "père" function occurring in the Dijkstra algorithm as presented in the INF 101 SDA course at Télécom ParisTech
    VertexInterface
    Modeling the vertex in a graph.
  • main使用的dijkstra中的类 
    类和说明
    VertexInterface
    Modeling the vertex in a graph.
  • maze使用的dijkstra中的类 
    类和说明
    GraphInterface
    Modeling the graph.
    VertexInterface
    Modeling the vertex in a graph.
